<h2>Essential Tips for the Drive</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Leave by 4:30–6:00 AM on weekends</strong> to avoid heavy SLEX traffic — Saturday and Sunday mornings can add 1–2 hours to your drive</li>
  <li>Use <strong>Waze or Google Maps</strong> for real-time traffic updates and the best route</li>
  <li>Bring <strong>EasyCard or RFID</strong> for SLEX and STAR Tollway to avoid cash lane queues</li>
  <li>Fuel up before leaving Manila — petrol stations in Calatagan may be limited</li>
  <li>Download offline maps for the final stretch to Calatagan in case of signal issues</li>
</ul>

<div class="callout">
  <p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> Book your floating cottage 2–3 days in advance, especially for weekends and Philippine holidays. Call or message the operator to confirm boat schedules the evening before your trip.</p>
